<br /></p>
<div style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/the-four-arcana/wheeltop.png" alt="wheeltop.png" class="image" /><br />
<span style="font-size:80%;"><em>在油火交织的海上，我漂流着，而我头顶，悬着那转轮。</em></span><br />
<img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/the-four-arcana/wheelbottom.png" alt="wheelbottom.png" class="image" /></div>
